des:
The Homeylux skill allows you to control your connected Homeylux devices with Alexa.
Monitor and control your Homeylux devices by using voice commands.

After connecting Alexa to your Homeylux products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Homeylux" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Homeylux account in our "Homeylux" app;
(3). You need to have some Homeylux devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Homeylux" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Homeylux" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Homeylux" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Homeylux", and you'll be navigated to Homeylux login page;
(9). Input your Homeylux account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
Once connected, you can use voice commands to interact with your Homeylux device. Some examples:

“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"

Keep an eye on the Homeylux skill as we'll be adding more features and products in the near future.
